HEADWORD: Nigrescent
<hw>Ni*gres"cent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>nigrescens</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>nigrescere</ets> to grow black,
fr. <ets>niger</ets> black. See <er>Negro</er>.]</ety> <def>Growing
black; changing to a black color; approaching to blackness.</def>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

